g angle strongly affects progress — VMG decreases when wind direction relative to the bow is less optimal.\n","\n","So what: Performance isn’t just about going fast; it’s about sailing in the right direction. Correct angle management is critical for efficiency.\n","\n","- ★ To maximise performance, a sailor must combine speed, apparent wind, and optimal angle — not just rely on wind strength."],"metadata":{"id":"QaxMCX2SvGdP"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["subset_cols = ['Speed Over The Ground', 'Speed Through Water', 'True Wind Speed', 'Apparent Wind Speed', 'Velocity Made Good']\n","pairplot_combined = combined[subset_cols]"],"metadata":{"id":"x0VecKsp76xt","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1773835494971,"user_tz":0,"elapsed":4,"user":{"displayName":"Emily Botting","userId":"04811858975560348602"}}},"execution_count":84,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["subset_cols = ['Speed Over The Ground', 'Speed Through Water', 'True Wind Speed', 'Apparent Wind Speed', 'Velocity Made Good', 'Session ID']\n","pairplot_combined = combined[subset_cols]\n","\n","sns.pairplot(pairplot_combined,\n"," hue='Session ID',\n"," diag_kind='hist')\n","\n","plt.suptitle('Pairplot of Sailing Speed Coloured by Boat Type', y=1.02)\n","\n","\n","plt.savefig(\"pairplot.png\")\n","\n","plt.show()"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":759},"id":"_CwWwDA88Mx4","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1773835504966,"user_tz":0,"elapsed":9997,"user":{"displayName":"Emily Botting","userId":"04811858975560348602"}},"outputId":"00f91a1b-4a0c-4458-8031-ab8b6f669d04"},"execution_count":85,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 1455.38x1250 with 30 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["(Data of SHADOW and Jengu Nab Tower is more spread out compared to Technative 1. This could suggest performance of Technative 1 is consistent and predictable compared to the two other boats. Th